---
title: Pulled Pork & Roasted Cherry Tomato Sub with Herby Fries, Salad & Hollandaise
description: Tired of eating shop-bought sandwiches? We know you are, so we’ve come up with a solution to rejuvenate your love for the sub
by packing it full of succulent pork and blistered cherry tomatoes that pop with juiciness. A helping of herb-infused fries to dip in
our garlic aioli and this is a sandwich you’ll never get bored of.

